content.p: Career After graduating, Farah did her internship at Cenergi SEA before getting absorbed into the organisation as a permanent employee. Currently, she is a Project Executive at the very organisation in the BioGas Project Delivery department which builds plants that convert waste to electricity. Farah does not have any plans to continue her studies at the moment, however, she is open to any opportunity arises. telephone: +6 (03) 8924 8000 fax: +6 (03) 8924 8018
